{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":90,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"小仲！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":187,"line_start":3,"line_end":3},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"你还有脸来见我！","tone":"沉声","chapter":187,"line_start":5,"line_end":5},{"speaker":"char_li_jing","speaker_name":"李靖","listener":null,"text":"我李靖究竟做过甚么事，令你在不见多年后，甫碰头便说这种话。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":187,"line_start":7,"line_end":9},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"做过甚么事阁下该心知肚明。枉我们当你是兄弟，你却为了讨好主子而出卖我们。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":187,"line_start":11,"line_end":13},{"speaker":"char_li_jing","speaker_name":"李靖","listener":null,"text":"我李靖是何等样人，怎会出卖兄弟朋友来求取宝名富贵？\n你给我说个清楚。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":187,"line_start":15,"line_end":17},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"若非你向李小子透露有关小陵拥有面具的事，李小子怎能那么肯定和氏璧是我们偷的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":19,"line_end":21},{"speaker":"char_li_jing","speaker_name":"李靖","listener":null,"text":"就算是我说的吧！\n但我真不明白偷和氏璧对你们有甚么好处？","tone":"苦笑","chapter":187,"line_start":23,"line_end":25},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"甚么叫就算是你说的，素姐的事我们很难和你计较，顶多说你不念恩情，贪新忘旧。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":187,"line_start":27,"line_end":29},{"speaker":"char_li_jing","speaker_name":"李靖","listener":null,"text":"闭嘴，你愈说愈过份了。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":187,"line_start":31,"line_end":31},{"speaker":"char_li_jing","speaker_name":"李靖","listener":null,"text":"无论你们怎样误会我，我始终当你和小陵是我的好兄弟，大家曾有过命的交情。\n而你可知道开罪了秦王的后果？","tone":"温柔","chapter":187,"line_start":37,"line_end":39},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"你最好再不要当我们是兄弟，否则你主子要你来对付我们时，你该如何处理？\n在眼前这时世里，只有朋友或敌人。唉！我也很少这么动气的，因为我一直信任你，而你却令我太失望了。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":187,"line_start":41,"line_end":45},{"speaker":"char_li_jing","speaker_name":"李靖","listener":null,"text":"不要在这件事上纠缠不清好吗？现在事情已到了最危险的边缘，一个不好，发生流血事件，事情便难以挽回。","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":47,"line_end":49},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"事情是打一开始便难以挽回。难道你现在仍天真得以为我们会交出和氏璧，再向李小子俯首称臣吗？\n你太小觑我寇仲哩。","tone":"疑问","chapter":187,"line_start":51,"line_end":53},{"speaker":"char_li_jing","speaker_name":"李靖","listener":null,"text":"我最清楚秦王的为人，处事果断，一旦认定了你是他敌人后，便会不惜一切来对付你。","tone":"沉声","chapter":187,"line_start":55,"line_end":57},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"我似乎比你更清楚李小子的心意：他怕李密远胜于怕我寇仲，所以李密一天未坍台，他亦未有馀兴对付我。","tone":"平静","chapter":187,"line_start":59,"line_end":61},{"speaker":"char_li_jing","speaker_name":"李靖","listener":null,"text":"你错啦，你和小陵都是能使他心存畏慕的人物。\n而且你们盗取和氏璧的方式亦太露锋芒了，更加深他的顾忌。\n何况你们还牵涉到'杨公宝库'这变数。唉！若你肯信我最后一趟，就立即离开洛阳，回到南方去，那你们说不定还可多过些风光日子。","tone":"无奈","chapter":187,"line_start":63,"line_end":69},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"我寇仲甚么风浪未经过，竟要你来提醒我。\n现在谁不想要我们的命，但我们仍不是过得轻松快活吗？","tone":"无奈","chapter":187,"line_start":71,"line_end":75},{"speaker":"char_li_jing","speaker_name":"李靖","listener":null,"text":"这只是你未曾和他正式交手吧。\n目下宁道奇和师妃暄这些正道的顶尖高手，都隐隐成了他的后盾，加上他本身的实力，天下已难有能撄其锋锐的人。\n而且你们羽翼未成，和他硬碰跟送死并没有分别。还是快点走吧！","tone":"认真","chapter":187,"line_start":77,"line_end":83},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"我走！不过却是走回自己的房间去。\n磨利你的剑吧！下次见面时，我们再非是兄弟。","tone":"大笑","chapter":187,"line_start":85,"line_end":87}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_kou_zhong","name":"寇仲","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"","personality":{"traits":["勇敢","机智","豪爽","忠诚","果断"],"speech_style":"","temperament":""},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":1,"line_end":90,"text":"第187章提及"}]},{"id":"char_li_jing","name":"李靖","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"","personality":{"traits":["勇敢","机智","豪爽","忠诚","果断"],"speech_style":"","temperament":""},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":1,"line_end":90,"text":"第187章提及"}]},{"id":"char_li_mi","name":"李密","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"","personality":{"traits":["勇敢","机智","豪爽","忠诚","果断"],"speech_style":"","temperament":""},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":1,"line_end":90,"text":"第187章提及"}]},{"id":"char_shi_fei_xuan","name":"师妃暄","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"","personality":{"traits":["勇敢","机智","豪爽","忠诚","果断"],"speech_style":"","temperament":""},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":1,"line_end":90,"text":"第187章提及"}]},{"id":"char_ning_dao_qi","name":"宁道奇","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"","personality":{"traits":["勇敢","机智","豪爽","忠诚","果断"],"speech_style":"","temperament":""},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":1,"line_end":90,"text":"第187章提及"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_luo_yang","name":"洛阳","region":"","one_line":"","source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":1,"line_end":90,"text":"第187章提及"}]}],"items":[{"id":"item_he_shi_bi","name":"和氏璧","type":"special","owner":null,"one_line":"","description":"和氏璧是江湖中传说的宝物，具有非凡的力量，各大势力争相夺取。","effects":[],"origin":"","rarity":"绝世神兵","related_characters":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":1,"line_end":90,"text":"第187章提及"}]},{"id":"item_yang_gong_bao_ku","name":"杨公宝库","type":"special","owner":null,"one_line":"","description":"杨公宝库是江湖中传说的宝物，具有非凡的力量，各大势力争相夺取。","effects":[],"origin":"","rarity":"绝世神兵","related_characters":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":1,"line_end":90,"text":"第187章提及"}]}]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":91,"line_end":269,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"寇仲在吗？","tone":"温柔","chapter":187,"line_start":91,"line_end":91},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"寇仲不在，但快回来，三小姐请进来坐坐。","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":93,"line_end":95},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"你和三小姐谈谈吧！我要到街上吸口新鲜空气。","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":101,"line_end":103},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"我是否打扰了你们呢？","tone":"犹豫","chapter":187,"line_start":109,"line_end":111},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"怎会呢？\n我们欢迎你还来不及。跋兄他只是另有要事，才趁机溜出去吧！","tone":"微笑","chapter":187,"line_start":113,"line_end":117},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"真想不到你们会和跋锋寒成为朋友，且他是那种对人情非常冷漠的人。","tone":"平静","chapter":187,"line_start":119,"line_end":121},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"你的变化比寇仲还要厉害！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":187,"line_start":123,"line_end":125},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"甚么变化？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":187,"line_start":127,"line_end":127},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"那是很难形容的一种变化，不但在外观上，还有气质，是种空灵剔透的感觉，《长生诀》确是非凡。","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":129,"line_end":131},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"三小姐似乎对寇仲相当关心？","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":133,"line_end":135},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"我若否认，便显得言不由衷。但请勿误会，我对你或寇仲并没有太大分别，或者是因为曾合作和交往过一段时间，又或因我欣赏你们的行事作风，所以总觉得你两人是玉致的朋友，会为你们担心注意。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":187,"line_start":139,"line_end":141},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"三小姐是消瘦了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":143,"line_end":143},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"你该知道，我是绝不会嫁给寇仲的。\n这心意从没有改变过。","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":145,"line_end":147},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"我还以为你对寇仲有不同寻常的观感哩！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":187,"line_start":149,"line_end":149},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"我们已不见多时，为何你会有这个想法？","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":151,"line_end":153},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"寇仲前晚在遇上你后，回来时满脸春风的样儿，所以才令我有这个错觉。","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":155,"line_end":157},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"我不但没有改变对他的看法和态度，还比以前更恨他。","tone":"无奈","chapter":187,"line_start":159,"line_end":161},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"更恨他？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":187,"line_start":163,"line_end":163},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"女人对一个男人是否真心诚意，会既挑剔又敏感。\n寇仲虽擅于甜言蜜语，但比对起他的行动，便很易发觉其口不对心的事实。","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":165,"line_end":169},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"三小姐从他甚么行动看出问题来？","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":171,"line_end":173},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"我可以告诉你，但你却须答应不转告寇仲才成。","tone":"严肃","chapter":187,"line_start":175,"line_end":175},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"好吧！我答应你。","tone":"无奈","chapter":187,"line_start":177,"line_end":177},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"他从来没有主动找我，更没有问过可如何找到我。\n若真是如他所说的着紧我，为何他没有想见人家的意欲呢？\n只从这点，便知他心里没有我。","tone":"淡然","chapter":187,"line_start":179,"line_end":183},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"可是玉致却不得不承认，和你们在一起时那感觉是既刺激又动人。\n唉！时间溜得可真快。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":187,"line_start":197,"line_end":199},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"你不是因此而来找寇仲吧？","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":201,"line_end":201},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"当然不是。今趟我是奉鲁叔之命而来，他想与你们见个面一叙旧情，不知你们明天是否有空？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":187,"line_start":203,"line_end":205},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"我也正想拜会他老人家，只因近来多事，自顾不暇，又不知他是否想见我们，才未敢打扰！","tone":"欣喜","chapter":187,"line_start":209,"line_end":211},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"那就不如明午在董家酒楼见面，厢房与酒席由我们安排。","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":213,"line_end":215},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"只要我们仍留得住性命，必不爽约。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":187,"line_start":217,"line_end":217},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"真不明白你们为何要弄得仇家遍地，希望你们不要变成杨广，人人要得之而甘心。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":187,"line_start":219,"line_end":221},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"或者因你们是非常人吧？\n每当所有人都认定你们难逃大劫时，你们总能轻轻松松的安然渡过危机，现在连鲁叔都要对你们刮目相看，重新估计。","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":225,"line_end":229},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"要不要我劝寇仲打消以'杨公宝库'作聘礼的念头？","tone":"温柔","chapter":187,"line_start":231,"line_end":233},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"我不知道，真的不知道。\n现在玉致的所有心思力气，都用在这件事上。若是没有了将会感觉到寂寞和失落。","tone":"低语","chapter":187,"line_start":235,"line_end":239},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"三小姐知否现在正愈陷愈深，至乎难以自拔？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":187,"line_start":241,"line_end":241},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"我不觉得。但终有一天，我要令寇仲知道我宋玉致是不会屈服的。\n且只会愈来愈恨他，他实在太可恶了。","tone":"认真","chapter":187,"line_start":243,"line_end":245},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"外人是不会明白我们家族的诸多规矩。\n以爹的情性，绝不会轻易把玉致许给非他自己选择的人，寇仲以为可用'杨公宝库'打动他，只是痴心妄想！","tone":"无奈","chapter":187,"line_start":247,"line_end":251},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"你定是觉得玉致自相矛盾，实情也是如此。\n唉！你和寇仲是如此不相同，究竟你是否也有心仪的女子？","tone":"微笑","chapter":187,"line_start":255,"line_end":259},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"我对男女之情非常淡薄，很少想到这方面的事。","tone":"犹豫","chapter":187,"line_start":261,"line_end":263},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":null,"text":"徐子陵若独身不娶，恐怕很多女子要失望哩！","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":265,"line_end":267}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xu_zi_ling","name":"徐子陵","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"","personality":{"traits":["勇敢","机智","豪爽","忠诚","果断"],"speech_style":"","temperament":""},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":91,"line_end":269,"text":"第187章提及"}]},{"id":"char_song_yu_zhi","name":"宋玉致","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"","personality":{"traits":["勇敢","机智","豪爽","忠诚","果断"],"speech_style":"","temperament":""},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":91,"line_end":269,"text":"第187章提及"}]},{"id":"char_ba_feng_han","name":"跋锋寒","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"","personality":{"traits":["勇敢","机智","豪爽","忠诚","果断"],"speech_style":"","temperament":""},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":91,"line_end":269,"text":"第187章提及"}]},{"id":"char_qu_ao","name":"曲傲","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"","personality":{"traits":["勇敢","机智","豪爽","忠诚","果断"],"speech_style":"","temperament":""},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start"