{"segment":3,"line_start":270,"line_end":346,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_song_jin_gang","speaker_name":"宋金刚","listener":null,"text":"我正要找寇兄，可巧竟在这处碰上。","tone":"大笑","chapter":187,"line_start":315,"line_end":317},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"真不好意思，由于俗务缠身，可否另约个时间再作详谈？","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":323,"line_end":325},{"speaker":"char_song_jin_gang","speaker_name":"宋金刚","listener":null,"text":"我正有此意。寇兄刚才与秦王是否有段不太愉快的接触？","tone":"微笑","chapter":187,"line_start":327,"line_end":329},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"你真的是有如目见，像一直吊在我背后的样子。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":187,"line_start":331,"line_end":331},{"speaker":"char_song_jin_gang","speaker_name":"宋金刚","listener":null,"text":"寇兄勿要误会，只是我手下见到寇兄与红拂女一道往秦王所在的厢房走去，现在又见寇兄气冲冲的下来，所以大胆揣测，寇兄莫要见怪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":187,"line_start":333,"line_end":335},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"是否翠儿领着曼清三花整个娘子军团杀到房里去，小陵你吃不消兜着走呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":187,"line_start":337,"line_end":339},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"少说废话，老跋可能已和曲老头打起来哩！","tone":"焦急","chapter":187,"line_start":341,"line_end":343}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_bi_xuan","name":"毕玄","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"","personality":{"traits":["勇敢","机智","豪爽","忠诚","果断"],"speech_style":"","temperament":""},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":270,"line_end":346,"text":"第187章提及"}]},{"id":"char_ba_dai_er","name":"芭黛儿","alias":[],"identity":"","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"","personality":{"traits":["勇敢","机智","豪爽","忠诚","果断"],"speech_style":"","temperament":""},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[187],"source_refs":[{"chapter":187,"line_start":270,"line_end":346,"text":"第187章提及"}]},{"id"